<title><![CDATA[Rioja Style Braised Potatoes with Chorizo and Pork Ribs]]></title>
<description><![CDATA[Pay attention to the way of splitting the potatoes by turning your knife sideways. This creates a jagged edge which will help your potatoes to lose more starch making this recipe even thicker and more delicious.

]]></description>
